OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGustavo Petro: Ex-rebel    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwins his coalition's       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fprimary                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Colombian Senator Gustavo Petro, who   
OL,6, polls suggest is the favourite to win  
OL,7, May's presidential election, has       
OL,8, secured the nomination of the left-wing
OL,9, Historic Pact coalition.               
OL,11,FMr Petro, a former guerrilla with the  
OL,12,FM-19 rebel group, won Sunday's primary 
OL,13,Fby a wide margin.                      
OL,15,FHe will face five other candidates in  
OL,16,Fthe presidential election on 29 May.   
OL,18,FWere he to win, Mr Petro would become  
OL,19,Fthe first left-wing president to lead  
OL,20,Fthe South American nation.             
